ef="https://www.nme.com/artists/freddie-gibbs">弗雷迪·吉布斯 (Freddie Gibbs)</a>和 Madlib <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/freddie-gibbs-madlib-announce-pinata-10th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3575360">将进行巡演以庆祝《皮纳塔》(Piñata) 十周年</a>。查看以下日期并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/freddie-gibbs-tickets/artist/1433139?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=U%3A4UeaTogxyPTxFx-k0T327XUkHznhQ5hRV8VU0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>获取剩余门票：</p><h3> <strong>Freddie Gibbs &amp; Madlib：Teñata – 10 Years of Piñata 2024 巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>可能</strong><br /><strong>10 – 马萨诸塞州波士顿@芬威米高梅音乐厅*</strong><br /> <strong>11 – 纽约，纽约 @ 17 号码头的屋顶 ^</strong><br /> <strong>19 - 芝加哥，伊利诺伊州@The Salt Shed *</strong></p><p> <strong>* = 带眼罩</strong><br /><strong>^ = 带粉色 Siifu</strong></p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madlib-joins-forces-with-black-thought-and-your-old-droog-with-new-single-reekyod-3752980">Madlib 与 Black Thought 和 Your Old Droog 联手推出新单曲“Reekyod”，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
